Class CommandParser

Object
  CommandParser

public class CommandParser
extends Object

Has a Director.

Creates a connection with Alfred. Once connection is established, CommandParser will start to receive commands from Alfred. Each command is parsed, grouped by action, and sent to Director so that the appropriate domain receives it. Messages from the domains go through here back to Alfred.

October 20, 2006
